{"tid":1927061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[拒絕非黑即白]爭取35+唔等於撐泛民 想幫本土派候選人就一定要做民意推動初選機制","createTime":"2020-03-15T14:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T15:25:10.000Z","uid":57911,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b76ce10b90b8a48f3ba88fa7ede000168ab87422","tid":1927061,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:01:27.000Z","msg":"如果想整走泛民首先唔係爭論議會外定議會內<br />\n而係大大力以民意嚟推動黃營初選機制<br />\n要知道泛民政棍其實蠢蠢欲動以黨內初選嚟取代黃營初選<br />\n密謀緊大石砸死蟹屈大家含撚含淚投啲覺得法治有險可守/暗暗哋撐派錢新移民<br />\n要謝絕依啲戰犯首先我哋要團結做個要求初選嘅民意出嚟先<br />\n而唔係鬼打鬼拗議會內定議會外啲咁低能嘅問題<br />\n選舉從來都唔係主線，而係一場向國際展示民意嘅公投"},{"pid":"44272b99f7ca7313d3a7a162f4614a1d89801ca9","tid":1927061,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4ff94ad50035f250029af0b953c705cf503545","tid":1927061,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4efed59d861df635563f7a49e75be3f2613d75a4","tid":1927061,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:03:34.000Z","msg":"【行動Post】請紀念苦難中的他和她，好好藉復活節將心意同文宣送到國際！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1926975\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1926975</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BM5PJdb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBM5PJdb.png&h=9cb80278&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V2XFPTb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV2XFPTb.png&h=9021aa23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d68f84b8d31bef11b5c98c68642217d95639a3b8","tid":1927061,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:04:47.000Z","msg":"Blcoked得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" 